parameters: Kru: "Are you okay?! There was a loud noise just now~"
Umi: "No-no, Kru! You can't come in!"
Kru: "What's wrong with just poking your head out?"
Umi: "Well... that... I'm naked... and it's embarrassing..."
Kru: "Come on, we're married... a little peek shouldn't..."
Umi: "Even if... we're married... it's still... embarrassing..."
Kru: "Well... I guess that's true but..."
Umi: "Ah... Ah! A droplet fell... it's cold... hah hah..."
Umi: "Uh... Ah... Yeah... hah hah... Ah..."
Kru: "Umi gets scared easily, after all."
Kru: "What's wrong? Your face is red, you know?"
Umi: "No... Ah... Maybe I'm just flushed... Mmm!"

Umi: "That's right... Kru... we're running low on groceries... Ugh... go
buy some!"
Kru: "I can do that, but... are you really okay?"
Kru: "Earlier in the forest, I saw a boar mating."
Umi: "Ahh... hah hah... Oh really... And then...?"
Kru: "And then... I watched for a bit. And you know what..."

Kru: "At first, the male was forcefully holding down the female, and he was
insisting on mating with her."

Kru: "The female was reluctant at first, but gradually she became more
aggressive."

Kru: "She started to move her hips in sync with the male's movements. And
after they finished, she chased after the male and insisted on mating
again."

Kru: "It was like... I was witnessing the wild. I thought humans wouldn't
become like that, and it made me laugh a bit."
Umi: "Hah... Really... That's... so... Ahh... Hah hah..."
Kru: "Well, I'm going to go now."
After that, I finished shopping and went home...

Even after I got home, Umi seemed to still be in the bath, making
clattering noises.
I prepared dinner while waiting for Umi to come out...
Kru "Ugh, Umi! What's with that outfit⁉"

Umi "Th-This is... supposedly the proper attire for a shrine maiden... I
have to wear it..."
Kru "Ah... sorry, I got a bit flustered..."

After that, we both felt somewhat awkward and spent time separately before
going to bed.
